  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Treatment of periodontal diseases is influenced by several risk factors. Psychological stress
      is considered as one of them. Aim of this study is to assess if stress influences results of
      non surgical periodontal treatment in severe chronic forms of periodontitis.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
